svg.text: This is the bus stop at Dean's Corners. The main road to Aylesbury and Arkham runs east to west respectively.
This is the Dunwich Turnoff. The main road to Aylesbury and Arkham runs east to west respectively. The road to Dunwich, little more than an improved dirt road, heads north.

This is a covered bridge made mainly of wooden planks. Dunwich Road continues to the north and south. A river flows east to west below the bridge.
